---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION_FR } from "../consts";
import { getCollection } from "astro:content";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Blog from "../components/Blog.astro";
---

<Layout title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION_FR}>
  <main>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="text-grid">
        <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
        <p>
          After bachelor of science in information sciences from Umeå
          University; one year studying Music for Cinema at Stockholm
          University; a course in Electric Engineering from Mittuniversitet, I
          have been spending most of my time making music and sound for theatre,
          contemporary dance, films and podcasts. As a musician I also release
          music with Old Amica and Folkvang.
        </p>
        <p>
          Last year I started the fullstack developer program from Altcademy to
          reinforce my coding skills to find job in the field of web design and
          web development. I have been writing some HTML / CSS / JS since I was
          a teenager (remember Dremweaver or customizing your friends MySpace
          profiles?) and in my work in theatre a good amount of MAX / MSP. But
          it was not until beginning of 2024 that I have started to seriously
          learn all that goes into being a web developer and learning some of
          the modern tools and frameworks that people uses today, including :
          Astro, React, Tailwind CSS, Ruby on Rails, Typescript.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you are looking for a developer for your next website or
          application, or a sound designer or mixer for your next project, get
          in touch.
        </p>
        <p>contact me: lnsjhnssn@gmail.com</p>
      </div>
      <div class="image-grid"></div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .grid-2 {
    margin: var(--space-xl) 0;
    /* max-width: 570px; */
    text-align: left;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(500px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-s);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .text-grid {
  }
</style>
